### Feature Modules

Each feature follows the standardized folder structure pattern:

- `page.tsx` - Main list/detail page
- `create/page.tsx` - Create page
- `[{id}]/` - Dynamic routes for details
- `_{feature}/` - Private feature folder with shared components

