## Important Notes

### React 19 Requirements

- Requires `npm install --force`
- Some peer dependency warnings are expected
- Latest React features supported

### Development Mode

- Set `NEXT_PUBLIC_DEV_MODE=true` for:
  - Source maps in production
  - React error overlay
  - Full URL logging in fetches

### Image Configuration

- Remote images from `s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com`
- SVG handling via `@svgr/webpack`

### Session Management

- Sessions handled via cookies
- JWT tokens managed server-side
- Automatic session refresh
- Protected routes via middleware

